I can't believe you're saying something like that.
Just so you know, there are plenty of magical

I don't know if you're some kind of savior or
what, but I can't treat you specially. It would be

Ugh... That's a harsh way to put it.

(By the way... It's really not good to give birth

end up giving birth. I wonder what kind of
adorable child will be born.
Just give birth without asking for permission.
What if it's a demon or a magical beast?

It seems the rule is to dispose of everything
except humans and LoliMon.

You don't seem interested... Well, I guess it
can't be helped.
Don't say things like that, it's cold.

What are you saying, even though you're a sinner?
Just because you're a magical girl, don't think
everything is forgiven.

It's so cold... Even though I brought a good story

I have no intention of listening to the story of a

Actually... I wanted to convey that I am very

That's true. It's a good thing, but even if you
convey that, it doesn't mean your sins will be
forgiven.

Well, don't say that. Despite how I may appear,
I've been reflecting a lot.

That's true. It's a good thing, but even if you
convey that, it doesn't mean your sins will be
lessened.

secretly... How about it?

How about a deal? If you let me out of here, all
of this will be yours.

H-Huh... It's not easy to obtain... Platinum
dust...

F-Fine... I'll secretly... let you take it out,
so... give it to me...
Negotiation successful, huh? Well then, go ahead.
